  "title": "Debris",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "summary": "A fully playable multi-level falling-block puzzle game for PRG32.",
  "description": "Debris is a Tetris-inspired PRG32 cartridge with player-controlled movement, rotation, hard and soft drops, hold, next-piece queue, scoring, line clears, pause, game-over restart, and speed that increases across levels. Graphics are procedural geometric blocks and the sound effects are synthesized/generated in code.",
